WEBVTT

00:34.430 --> 00:35.290
Your Highness,

00:36.110 --> 00:37.030
why is it you?

00:38.280 --> 00:39.350
I didn't kill Xu.

00:40.900 --> 00:42.430
It wasn't me who killed him.

00:43.640 --> 00:44.640
You wicked woman.

00:45.670 --> 00:47.670
During the incident at Xuri Palace,

00:48.470 --> 00:52.030
I risked my life to protect you and Xu,

00:52.750 --> 00:55.350
but you ended up in Li Jiao's bed.

00:55.720 --> 00:57.170
For the throne,

00:57.790 --> 01:00.280
Li Jiao wouldn't even
spare my child left behind.

01:00.280 --> 01:02.560
He will come to a bad end,

01:03.110 --> 01:04.680
and so will you.

01:05.610 --> 01:06.300
No!

01:07.120 --> 01:07.920
Your Majesty!

01:09.070 --> 01:09.870
Your Majesty!

01:10.510 --> 01:11.310
Your Majesty.

01:11.870 --> 01:13.600
Did you have a nightmare again?

01:14.640 --> 01:15.200
I'm fine.

01:22.430 --> 01:23.820
[Li Jiao]

01:25.920 --> 01:26.720
Your Majesty,

01:27.430 --> 01:28.830
I'm sorry for being late.

01:37.570 --> 01:38.789
You had a dream again?

01:40.789 --> 01:41.850
It was just a dream.

01:42.640 --> 01:44.039
Don't take it seriously.

01:44.870 --> 01:45.590
Ziyu,

01:46.680 --> 01:48.710
do you think I am terrifying?

01:49.470 --> 01:53.150
I'm carving a memorial tablet
for my husband while he is still alive,

01:53.150 --> 01:54.840
and I showed no mercy

01:55.590 --> 01:56.759
to my own child.

01:57.710 --> 01:59.440
I have never had such a thought.

02:01.120 --> 02:02.780
You are wise and intelligent.

02:03.510 --> 02:06.040
You know what is most important
in this palace

02:06.400 --> 02:07.560
and what is not.

02:08.240 --> 02:10.560
I never wanted to hurt my own child.

02:12.240 --> 02:13.360
For so many years,

02:14.840 --> 02:16.500
I've been putting up with him.

02:17.030 --> 02:19.630
As long as he obediently remains
a useless man,

02:21.240 --> 02:23.560
I can guarantee him a peaceful life.

02:24.079 --> 02:26.079
His Highness is reckless at his age.

02:27.280 --> 02:29.470
Please don't let him ruin your health.

02:34.710 --> 02:35.510
You're wrong.

02:36.150 --> 02:37.710
Do you think I would believe

02:38.910 --> 02:40.910
that what the Crown Prince did today

02:42.030 --> 02:44.160
was because he truly loves that woman?

02:44.740 --> 02:46.250
To men, women

02:47.150 --> 02:48.610
can satisfy their desires

02:49.190 --> 02:50.990
and continue their family line.

02:51.320 --> 02:52.480
Men need women

02:53.230 --> 02:54.440
and dote on them.

02:55.470 --> 02:58.910
They would decorate them
with gold and jewels,

02:59.670 --> 03:02.440
and entice them with sweet words.

03:03.240 --> 03:04.750
But they would never

03:05.120 --> 03:06.920
truly risk anything for a woman.

03:10.080 --> 03:10.750
Men...

03:11.150 --> 03:13.050
can only be seduced by power

03:13.910 --> 03:15.470
and take risks for it.

03:16.590 --> 03:18.920
What that woman brings to the Crown Prince

03:18.950 --> 03:20.520
is definitely not just love.

03:20.520 --> 03:22.079
They must be plotting

03:23.180 --> 03:24.700
against me.

03:37.910 --> 03:38.680
Zhen,

03:40.280 --> 03:42.360
I will uncover the truth for you.

05:05.980 --> 05:11.270
[REBIRTH]

05:11.780 --> 05:14.320
[Episode 8]

05:22.630 --> 05:23.310
Chun'er,

05:24.000 --> 05:25.060
what are you doing?

05:25.310 --> 05:26.160
Leaving here.

05:26.480 --> 05:27.240
Leaving you.

05:28.040 --> 05:28.870
Why?

05:31.310 --> 05:31.950
Li Yan,

05:32.170 --> 05:33.970
you're not some ordinary man.

05:34.800 --> 05:37.070
You are the Prince of Luo in Biantang,
a royal descendant.

05:37.070 --> 05:38.800
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

05:38.830 --> 05:39.750
I don't want to have anything to do

05:39.750 --> 05:41.480
with the royal family anymore!

05:43.390 --> 05:44.000
Chun'er!

05:45.630 --> 05:46.240
Chun'er.

05:47.070 --> 05:48.070
I told you

05:48.720 --> 05:49.920
that my name is Li Yan.

05:50.510 --> 05:52.870
After my father passed away,
I observed 3 years of mourning.

05:52.870 --> 05:54.630
I stay away from court affairs
and enjoy farming and studying.

05:54.630 --> 05:55.690
All of this is true.

05:58.720 --> 05:59.870
It's true that I never told you

05:59.870 --> 06:01.400
about my status as a prince,

06:01.920 --> 06:03.430
but that's because my father,
the Prince of Chang,

06:03.430 --> 06:05.600
was suspected by Biantang Emperor
in his early years.

06:05.600 --> 06:07.070
He was confined in Jincheng his whole life

06:07.070 --> 06:08.400
and died of depression.

06:08.720 --> 06:09.950
As his son,

06:10.310 --> 06:12.040
although I inherited the title of prince,

06:12.040 --> 06:13.680
I could only live in seclusion
observing mourning,

06:13.680 --> 06:16.430
and without an imperial decree,
I could not enter the capital.

06:16.430 --> 06:17.380
I know very well

06:17.830 --> 06:19.830
that I am not of high royal blood.

06:20.430 --> 06:22.120
I just wanted to face you

06:22.360 --> 06:23.270
as Li Yan.

06:24.870 --> 06:26.720
There's no use saying this now.

06:27.310 --> 06:28.160
In my eyes,

06:28.680 --> 06:30.000
you are the Prince of Luo,

06:30.000 --> 06:31.570
and that makes you royal.

06:31.870 --> 06:33.850
Whether you are in power or favored,

06:33.850 --> 06:35.909
you are worlds apart from commoners.

06:38.070 --> 06:38.600
Chun'er.

06:39.159 --> 06:40.690
Then can you at least tell me

06:41.120 --> 06:43.430
why you hate the royal family so much?

06:45.720 --> 06:47.390
Because all nobles

06:47.600 --> 06:49.360
surround themselves with concubines,

06:49.360 --> 06:50.580
and the beautiful female slaves
around them

06:50.580 --> 06:51.720
are countless.

06:51.950 --> 06:53.010
I can't stand this.

06:53.270 --> 06:54.750
I don't want to have anything to do with

06:54.750 --> 06:55.950
the sons of noble families anymore.

06:55.950 --> 06:56.560
Chun'er!

06:58.510 --> 06:59.310
Wait a minute.

07:03.870 --> 07:04.830
From today on,

07:05.360 --> 07:06.820
you are free from slavery.

07:07.040 --> 07:09.220
Whether you want to go home
or get married,

07:09.220 --> 07:10.510
it's all up to you.

07:11.000 --> 07:13.400
This money is enough for you
to settle down.

07:13.600 --> 07:15.240
We were master and servants once,

07:15.240 --> 07:16.700
but we will part ways here.

07:16.920 --> 07:18.450
You can live a free life now.

07:19.680 --> 07:24.510
-Thank you, Your Highness!
-Thank you, Your Highness!

07:24.510 --> 07:25.360
Come and get the money.

07:25.360 --> 07:26.820
Thank you, Your Highness!

07:29.380 --> 07:30.840
Thank you, Your Highness.

07:33.390 --> 07:34.850
Thank you, Your Highness.

07:39.720 --> 07:41.180
Thank you, Your Highness.

07:43.720 --> 07:45.180
Thank you, Your Highness.

07:47.390 --> 07:48.850
Thank you, Your Highness.

08:04.820 --> 08:06.280
Thank you, Your Highness.

08:15.560 --> 08:17.020
Thank you, Your Highness.

08:35.150 --> 08:35.750
Chunxing,

08:36.200 --> 08:37.600
you don't want the money?

08:42.789 --> 08:43.750
Your Highness!

08:45.030 --> 08:46.790
I was sold here when I was little.

08:46.790 --> 08:48.630
I know nothing else but to serve you!

08:48.630 --> 08:49.940
Please let me stay.

08:49.970 --> 08:51.220
I am willing to work like a dog

08:51.220 --> 08:53.150
to serve you for the rest of my life!

08:59.200 --> 08:59.840
Okay.

09:00.280 --> 09:01.280
Then you can stay.

09:04.910 --> 09:08.360
Thank you, Your Highness!
Thank you, Your Highness!

09:09.110 --> 09:10.640
Mozhan, what are you doing?

09:10.960 --> 09:11.440
I...

09:11.900 --> 09:13.180
I also want to spend my whole life

09:13.180 --> 09:14.910
working like a dog to serve you.

09:21.280 --> 09:22.430
Both of you can stay.

09:28.200 --> 09:29.200
You may leave too.

09:29.320 --> 09:29.790
Yes.

09:32.720 --> 09:34.270
I am also willing to work like a dog

09:34.270 --> 09:36.200
to serve you for the rest of my life.

09:36.840 --> 09:38.300
Thank you, Your Highness.

09:41.960 --> 09:43.870
If only Yan Xun...

09:45.510 --> 09:46.570
could be like this.

09:47.030 --> 09:47.750
Chun'er,

09:48.200 --> 09:49.720
what are you talking about?

09:49.720 --> 09:51.030
Why did you do this?

09:51.360 --> 09:52.270
You are not him.

09:52.270 --> 09:53.840
What's the use of doing all this?

09:53.840 --> 09:54.440
Chun'er,

09:54.910 --> 09:55.870
what's wrong?

10:01.120 --> 10:01.750
Chun'er!

10:42.120 --> 10:44.450
This is the third thing Qiao promised you,

10:44.790 --> 10:46.450
the portrait of Fu you wanted.

10:46.640 --> 10:49.900
Thank you for your help
at the palace banquet the other day.

10:54.390 --> 10:56.390
This portrait was kept in the palace.

10:56.390 --> 10:57.990
How did Your Highness get it?

10:58.000 --> 10:59.800
I am the Crown Prince, after all.

10:59.840 --> 11:02.640
I just spent some money
and got it out of the palace.

11:06.750 --> 11:09.360
But I have another question.

11:09.480 --> 11:10.870
Please go ahead, Your Highness.

11:10.870 --> 11:12.200
Why did you help us?

11:13.280 --> 11:15.410
Your situation is no better than mine.

11:15.600 --> 11:17.510
Is it just because of this portrait?

11:17.510 --> 11:18.510
Aren't you afraid

11:18.960 --> 11:21.290
of getting into trouble with the Empress?

11:21.870 --> 11:22.730
Your Highness,

11:24.120 --> 11:26.150
do you remember when we were young?

11:26.600 --> 11:27.510
Of course I do.

11:29.270 --> 11:31.670
We both fell in love with Fu
at the same time,

11:32.000 --> 11:33.440
and even fought over her.

11:33.960 --> 11:34.630
Yes.

11:35.120 --> 11:36.920
We were very childish back then.

11:40.910 --> 11:41.750
But actually,

11:42.480 --> 11:43.300
I've always felt there was a

11:43.300 --> 11:45.230
mutual understanding between us.

11:45.550 --> 11:47.200
To say something presumptuous,

11:47.200 --> 11:48.080
you and I

11:49.030 --> 11:50.480
have suffered alike.

11:51.550 --> 11:53.390
When His Majesty ascended the throne,

11:53.390 --> 11:54.720
because my father
and Crown Prince Maocheng

11:54.720 --> 11:56.320
were born to the same mother,

11:56.320 --> 11:59.270
he was ordered to live in seclusion
in the remote Jincheng.

11:59.270 --> 12:00.930
Later, my father passed away.

12:02.750 --> 12:04.150
I was 14 then,

12:05.000 --> 12:07.130
coming to Tangjing for the first time.

12:07.870 --> 12:10.120
To show his magnanimity and compassion,

12:10.120 --> 12:12.360
His Majesty made an exception
and made me a Prince.

12:12.360 --> 12:13.420
Though I was young,

12:13.720 --> 12:14.870
I knew very well

12:15.560 --> 12:17.630
that even a eunuch

12:18.130 --> 12:19.550
or a maid by the Empress's side

12:19.550 --> 12:21.080
had more power than me

12:21.650 --> 12:23.580
and could hold their heads higher.

12:24.120 --> 12:24.720
Li Yan,

12:26.240 --> 12:27.170
all these years,

12:28.840 --> 12:30.970
I know you must have had a hard time too.

12:34.390 --> 12:35.250
Your Highness,

12:35.530 --> 12:36.050
do you remember

12:36.050 --> 12:38.110
the day Fu went to war with her father?

12:40.910 --> 12:41.670
I do.

12:42.270 --> 12:43.630
It was raining that day.

12:44.030 --> 12:45.760
We went to see her off together,

12:45.870 --> 12:48.600
all the way to more than 30 miles
outside the city.

12:48.960 --> 12:51.760
You were completely soaked
but refused to go back.

12:52.100 --> 12:53.960
Actually, I had a chance back then

12:54.720 --> 12:56.120
to plead with the Empress

12:56.630 --> 12:58.480
to let Fu stay and marry me.

12:58.630 --> 13:01.030
But because I was concerned
about my status

13:01.070 --> 13:03.200
and feared the Empress, I didn't dare.

13:04.320 --> 13:06.630
So I missed the only chance

13:08.110 --> 13:09.510
to save her.

13:12.230 --> 13:13.760
Last night in the main hall,

13:14.270 --> 13:15.270
somehow,

13:15.780 --> 13:17.660
I felt like I was back to that day,

13:18.510 --> 13:20.570
the day we saw Fu off from the capital.

13:22.060 --> 13:22.870
I felt

13:23.080 --> 13:25.340
this was heaven giving me another chance

13:25.890 --> 13:27.220
to make up for my regret.

13:29.960 --> 13:30.630
That's why

13:32.160 --> 13:33.630
you wanted to help us?

13:34.150 --> 13:35.680
I have missed my chance once

13:36.600 --> 13:38.320
and lost Fu forever.

13:38.730 --> 13:39.390
But I don't want

13:39.390 --> 13:41.460
the tragedy to repeat itself on you.

13:56.670 --> 13:58.470
Even if you have to break the ice,

13:58.750 --> 14:00.480
you must find her!

14:13.630 --> 14:14.430
Your Majesty!

14:14.480 --> 14:15.790
Lady Chu fell into the lake a month ago.

14:15.790 --> 14:16.870
The frozen lake spans thousands of miles,

14:16.870 --> 14:18.270
and the ice on the surface never melts.

14:18.270 --> 14:19.390
Breaking it open

14:19.390 --> 14:20.600
might be impossible.

14:27.360 --> 14:28.160
Your Majesty,

14:28.320 --> 14:30.240
we found an underground river nearby,

14:30.240 --> 14:31.300
leading to Ximeng.

14:31.620 --> 14:32.550
This ornament

14:32.600 --> 14:34.600
was found by the underground river.

14:37.000 --> 14:38.270
Chu is not dead.

14:41.080 --> 14:42.870
You must find her!

14:49.960 --> 14:52.000
Arrest the manager of this store!

14:52.150 --> 14:52.870
Yes!

14:58.290 --> 14:58.800
Move!

15:04.880 --> 15:06.030
Have you seen Chu?

15:06.750 --> 15:07.670
If she's still alive,

15:07.670 --> 15:08.840
she will definitely try to contact

15:08.840 --> 15:10.570
your Universal Harmony Guild.

15:18.670 --> 15:20.870
The Universal Harmony Guild
has long been gone,

15:20.870 --> 15:22.070
but you have a family,

15:22.510 --> 15:24.120
a wife, children, and parents.

15:24.120 --> 15:25.240
If you don't know,

15:25.840 --> 15:28.480
I will personally ask your family

15:28.510 --> 15:29.590
to see who

15:30.960 --> 15:32.240
is willing to tell me.

15:32.320 --> 15:33.480
Yan Xun,

15:34.540 --> 15:37.180
you ungrateful wretch!

15:38.520 --> 15:41.760
Without the help
of the Universal Harmony Guild,

15:42.270 --> 15:45.360
how could you have escaped

15:45.360 --> 15:46.890
from Great Yong, that hell?

15:46.960 --> 15:49.420
It wasn't enough
that you killed Miss Zhong,

15:50.000 --> 15:52.670
and you won't even let go of Lady Chu.

15:53.470 --> 15:54.410
What did you say?

15:55.510 --> 15:56.770
Who killed Miss Zhong?

15:57.510 --> 16:00.670
Did you use Miss Zhong
to lure Lady Chu out

16:01.220 --> 16:03.770
just to kill them all?

16:04.720 --> 16:07.150
Fortunately, heaven showed mercy

16:07.720 --> 16:09.630
and let Lady Chu survive.

16:10.480 --> 16:13.210
Not to mention
that I don't know where Lady Chu is.

16:13.720 --> 16:15.240
Even if I did,

16:15.550 --> 16:18.750
I would never tell you.

17:01.360 --> 17:02.440
Congratulations, Your Majesty!

17:02.440 --> 17:04.569
Your martial skills are even better
than before your recovery.

17:04.569 --> 17:06.170
Chu Qiao, that femme fatale,

17:06.440 --> 17:08.109
leaving Great Yan is a great fortune

17:08.109 --> 17:09.589
for both you and Great Yan.

17:22.200 --> 17:23.660
Cheng Yuan, let me ask you.

17:24.589 --> 17:26.480
Why can't you let go of Chu?

17:27.140 --> 17:28.270
Over and over again,

17:28.290 --> 17:30.820
you betrayed and disobeyed me
because of Chu.

17:30.960 --> 17:32.510
Your Majesty, in my heart,

17:32.830 --> 17:34.090
you're the only King of Great Yan.

17:34.090 --> 17:34.860
I have never betrayed you.

17:34.860 --> 17:35.860
You told me

17:36.160 --> 17:38.290
that Zhong Yu died suddenly in prison,

17:38.950 --> 17:40.570
but it was actually you who killed her

17:40.570 --> 17:41.830
and used her to kill Chu.

17:41.830 --> 17:43.360
You think I don't know that?

17:50.680 --> 17:51.480
Your Majesty,

17:52.480 --> 17:53.480
kill me.

17:54.310 --> 17:57.400
Chu Qiao will only be a stumbling block
on your path to revenge!

17:57.400 --> 17:58.030
She...

17:58.750 --> 17:59.750
must die.

17:59.960 --> 18:01.000
I will not spare

18:01.000 --> 18:03.030
anyone who hurts Chu.

18:04.830 --> 18:06.200
And I won't keep you.

18:11.960 --> 18:13.720
I don't want to see you again

18:41.480 --> 18:42.340
Close the door.

18:57.240 --> 18:58.240
Close the window.

19:07.440 --> 19:08.640
This is a Xuanji Bell.

19:09.160 --> 19:11.090
There used to be many in Qingshan Manor.

19:11.090 --> 19:12.790
It sounds like an ordinary wind chime,

19:12.790 --> 19:14.240
but it's extremely penetrating.

19:14.240 --> 19:15.680
It can be heard for miles.

19:16.030 --> 19:18.490
If someone comes uninvited
to your mansion,

19:18.880 --> 19:20.160
I can hear the noise.

19:25.400 --> 19:26.730
There is one more thing,

19:27.000 --> 19:28.480
and it's the most important.

19:28.480 --> 19:29.240
What is it?

19:40.160 --> 19:41.680
It doesn't matter
that you don't know martial arts.

19:41.680 --> 19:42.960
I'll teach you three moves.

19:42.960 --> 19:44.830
At a critical moment,
they can not only save your life,

19:44.830 --> 19:46.360
but maybe also save others.

19:46.830 --> 19:49.550
The move just now is called
"Two Dragons Playing with a Pearl."

19:49.550 --> 19:52.280
It's for when someone attacks you
from the front.

19:53.000 --> 19:54.430
You can use it to injure the enemy's eyes,

19:54.430 --> 19:56.090
buying you a chance to escape.

19:57.920 --> 19:58.640
Try it.

20:10.340 --> 20:12.720
This move is called
"Divine Dragon Wagging Its Tail."

20:12.720 --> 20:15.250
It's for when someone
tries to sneak up on you.

20:17.480 --> 20:18.240
Good move.

20:18.670 --> 20:19.930
There's one last move.

20:20.830 --> 20:21.630
The last move.

20:31.030 --> 20:31.960
Awesome!

20:33.880 --> 20:35.070
What is this move called?

20:35.070 --> 20:36.120
It's called...

20:36.440 --> 20:37.770
"the Quick-Foot Flee."

20:38.400 --> 20:39.400
Commonly known as

20:40.000 --> 20:40.930
"Running Fast."

20:41.920 --> 20:43.000
"Running Fast"?

20:43.480 --> 20:45.070
You don't have any foundation
in martial arts.

20:45.070 --> 20:46.040
No matter how much I teach you,

20:46.040 --> 20:48.110
you won't be able
to master it in a short time.

20:48.110 --> 20:49.030
The key is

20:49.450 --> 20:50.760
that when you encounter danger,

20:50.760 --> 20:52.420
you need to be able to run away.

20:53.480 --> 20:54.720
Don't sleep tonight.

20:55.030 --> 20:57.090
Practice these three moves 30 times.

20:57.830 --> 20:58.830
Thirty?

20:59.590 --> 21:02.390
Is this also something
you learned from Zhuge Yue?

21:02.480 --> 21:03.680
He doesn't need this.

21:43.010 --> 21:44.610
It's Lord Zhan's order.

21:51.440 --> 21:52.400
Yes, My Lord.

23:21.830 --> 23:24.310
Princess, you are here?

23:25.110 --> 23:26.400
We thought

23:26.830 --> 23:27.920
you weren't here.

23:27.920 --> 23:30.000
We just wanted to come and see you.

23:30.350 --> 23:32.920
Why are you so cruel to us?

23:33.270 --> 23:34.070
See me?

23:35.350 --> 23:36.960
Sneaking around to see me?

23:37.200 --> 23:37.880
Yes.

23:40.940 --> 23:43.590
You misunderstood, Princess.

23:43.720 --> 23:46.200
We just wanted
to come and play games with you.

23:46.200 --> 23:47.550
We thought you weren't here,

23:47.550 --> 23:49.610
so we dared to come in and look around.

24:18.040 --> 24:20.250
♪ The flowers fall into the sleeves ♪

24:20.370 --> 24:22.910
♪ They do not understand my sorrow ♪

24:23.350 --> 24:24.650
♪ With a pot of wine ♪

24:24.670 --> 24:26.130
♪ My longing surges ♪

24:26.160 --> 24:28.670
♪ I become haggard ♪

24:29.280 --> 24:31.720
♪ Light rain falls on the window ♪

24:31.760 --> 24:34.580
♪ Awakening from the dream,
I no longer know what year it is ♪

24:34.600 --> 24:36.310
♪ Love never stops ♪

24:36.610 --> 24:39.990
♪ Yet we are already far apart ♪

24:40.010 --> 24:42.280
♪ What I seek in life ♪

24:42.310 --> 24:43.890
♪ Is nothing more
than to look back once more ♪

24:43.920 --> 24:46.500
♪ With the fragrance still lingering ♪

24:46.530 --> 24:48.110
♪ The shaking hands ♪

24:48.140 --> 24:51.320
♪ Are still hiding affection ♪

24:51.350 --> 24:53.710
♪ Words left unspoken ♪

24:53.730 --> 24:55.240
♪ Turn into guilt ♪

24:55.270 --> 24:57.920
♪ Hidden in the stars ♪

24:57.950 --> 25:02.810
♪ Rippling throughout this life ♪

25:02.830 --> 25:04.230
♪ I ask the vast sky ♪

25:04.250 --> 25:06.500
♪ The wind is light,
but my longing is heavy ♪

25:06.530 --> 25:08.970
♪ How to start over ♪

25:08.990 --> 25:12.310
♪ How do we love
and hold on without parting ♪

25:12.330 --> 25:14.590
♪ Without misunderstandings? ♪

25:14.610 --> 25:18.020
♪ Do not let me only understand
the meaning of a fleeting glance ♪

25:18.050 --> 25:20.360
♪ When my eyes are red with tears ♪

25:20.390 --> 25:23.270
♪ What cannot be kept,
can only be sent away ♪

25:23.290 --> 25:27.830
♪ In the end ♪

25:29.470 --> 25:34.850
♪ It can only be praised ♪

26:11.030 --> 26:12.430
Where is your King Li'an?

26:12.830 --> 26:14.030
Since he has been defeated,

26:14.030 --> 26:15.510
why doesn't he come out of the city
to welcome King Ximeng?

26:15.510 --> 26:17.440
Our King knows his sins are grave.

26:17.440 --> 26:19.000
He sincerely wants to surrender to Ximeng.

26:19.000 --> 26:20.600
He has now taken off his armor

26:20.720 --> 26:23.180
and is waiting for punishment
in the prison.

26:38.750 --> 26:42.150
Please enter the city, King Ximeng,
to receive his respects.

27:26.240 --> 27:27.720
Where is your king?

27:28.270 --> 27:29.930
Bring him out for an audience.

28:33.310 --> 28:34.110
King Ximeng!

28:34.460 --> 28:37.130
You will die in Li'an City today!

30:29.960 --> 30:30.690
You go first.

30:31.330 --> 30:31.960
General!

30:31.990 --> 30:33.570
King Ximeng
has surrounded us with his army!

30:33.570 --> 30:34.700
We've been tricked!

30:35.170 --> 30:38.200
That old bastard King Ximeng
used this brat to lure us away.

30:38.200 --> 30:39.570
Our plan failed.

30:40.080 --> 30:42.430
Then let's take this brat down with us!

30:49.500 --> 30:50.110
Go!

30:54.950 --> 30:58.020
I want him to be my shadow,

30:58.360 --> 31:01.990
to act as a decoy
in Li'an City in my place.

31:33.270 --> 31:36.180
♪ We mock karma ♪

31:37.110 --> 31:39.680
♪ For being unfair ♪

31:40.100 --> 31:42.090
♪ Why is life ♪

31:42.340 --> 31:46.390
♪ Often filled with regrets? ♪

31:48.160 --> 31:50.600
♪ The snow falls ♪

31:51.000 --> 31:54.180
♪ With fate ♪

31:55.010 --> 31:56.250
♪ It will eventually ♪

31:56.710 --> 31:58.710
♪ Fall before ♪

31:58.730 --> 32:01.190
♪ The dawn ♪

32:01.670 --> 32:03.880
♪ As a foreigner ♪

32:04.050 --> 32:08.590
♪ Don't look, don't ask, and don't speak ♪

32:08.880 --> 32:11.160
♪ Wander ♪

32:11.380 --> 32:15.580
♪ With no resentment at all ♪

32:16.070 --> 32:18.310
♪ The lock in my heart ♪

32:18.500 --> 32:19.940
♪ Put the memories ♪

32:19.960 --> 32:23.840
♪ In the silence of the night ♪

32:24.240 --> 32:25.250
♪ Wait ♪

32:25.810 --> 32:30.570
♪ For the stars and moon
to part ways again ♪

32:30.590 --> 32:32.800
♪ As a foreigner ♪

32:32.980 --> 32:37.520
♪ Don't look, don't ask, and don't speak ♪

32:37.810 --> 32:40.080
♪ Wander ♪

32:40.300 --> 32:44.510
♪ With no resentment at all ♪

32:45.160 --> 32:47.260
♪ Traveling alone ♪

32:47.570 --> 32:49.560
♪ In a world ♪

32:49.580 --> 32:53.140
♪ Where fate is unkind ♪

32:53.170 --> 32:54.340
♪ Look ♪

32:54.750 --> 32:58.950
♪ The mortal world has forgotten me ♪

33:00.500 --> 33:02.040
♪ I wish ♪

33:02.510 --> 33:09.470
♪ You'll forget me ♪

33:04.830 --> 33:05.720
Xing...

33:07.720 --> 33:09.680
I can't hold on anymore.

33:19.200 --> 33:20.030
Zhuge Yue,

33:20.880 --> 33:21.750
you taught me

33:22.830 --> 33:24.790
that no matter what situation we're in,

33:24.790 --> 33:26.450
as long as we're not defeated,

33:26.720 --> 33:28.040
we can be reborn.

33:44.410 --> 33:46.980
♪ Facing the wind, I tread through frost ♪

33:46.310 --> 33:47.070
Zhuge Yue...

33:47.000 --> 33:50.140
♪ Measuring rivers and hills,
hooves rise light ♪

33:49.550 --> 33:50.640
stay alive.

33:50.810 --> 33:53.390
♪ The horizon lies far ahead ♪

33:51.270 --> 33:52.200
Xing...

33:53.550 --> 33:55.640
♪ Swaying gently ♪

33:53.750 --> 33:54.680
You taught me

33:55.680 --> 33:57.750
that we should stay alive
even in the dark.

33:57.750 --> 33:59.980
♪ Through pine mists, past 1,000 hills ♪

34:00.010 --> 34:03.400
♪ Wrapped in the vast moonlight ♪

34:01.830 --> 34:03.690
Let's fight our way out together.

34:04.070 --> 34:06.790
♪ Having drunk the surging waves ♪

34:06.810 --> 34:09.440
♪ I care not how far the road ♪

34:11.360 --> 34:13.770
♪ When I was young ♪

34:13.389 --> 34:14.270
Xing,

34:13.790 --> 34:16.850
♪ I wrote poems
praising the prosperous world ♪

34:15.480 --> 34:16.810
let's fight our way out!

34:17.130 --> 34:20.290
♪ The wind was not yet full,
the moon not yet round ♪

34:20.320 --> 34:24.350
♪ Rushing me to charge forward ♪

34:25.310 --> 34:26.920
♪ Strong wine to the wild plains ♪

34:26.940 --> 34:28.750
♪ Beyond the pass,
sand blows like arrows ♪

34:28.840 --> 34:30.130
♪ I ride and whip my steed ♪

34:30.290 --> 34:32.100
♪ Chasing 10,000 miles of cloud and mist ♪

34:32.130 --> 34:33.580
♪ Mountains and rivers fade behind ♪

34:33.600 --> 34:35.600
♪ The wind crowns me ♪

34:35.620 --> 34:38.570
♪ Your eyes glow with flame ♪

34:38.610 --> 34:40.420
♪ Strong wind breaks the lute strings ♪

34:40.449 --> 34:42.290
♪ Playing for 5,000 years ♪

34:42.310 --> 34:43.820
♪ I ride my horse toward the south ♪

34:43.850 --> 34:45.600
♪ Endless spring beneath my hooves ♪

34:45.630 --> 34:47.020
♪ Hoofbeats fade away ♪

34:47.250 --> 34:48.810
♪ Rolling over peaks and ridges ♪

34:48.900 --> 34:52.110
♪ A single neigh echoes
between heaven and earth ♪

34:52.130 --> 34:54.080
♪ Treading on the clear wind ♪

34:55.310 --> 34:57.370
♪ The realm unfolds like a scroll ♪

34:58.410 --> 35:00.410
♪ Chasing the bright moon ♪

35:01.950 --> 35:05.120
♪ My spirit swallows
mountains and rivers ♪

35:09.800 --> 35:10.400
Qiao,

35:10.760 --> 35:11.550
you got hurt?

35:12.510 --> 35:13.320
Great!

35:14.480 --> 35:16.080
I can finally pick up a sword!

35:16.960 --> 35:17.840
Zhuge Yue,

35:18.630 --> 35:19.710
I did it!

35:50.330 --> 35:51.990
Please forgive me, Lord Zhan.

35:52.120 --> 35:53.510
That woman is very alert.

35:53.510 --> 35:54.480
We tested her several times,

35:54.480 --> 35:56.340
but she didn't give herself away.

35:56.360 --> 35:58.440
People are alert when awake,

35:59.150 --> 36:01.070
but not necessarily...

36:01.690 --> 36:03.150
when on the verge of death.

36:22.460 --> 36:23.100
Help!

36:24.150 --> 36:25.000
Help!

36:29.510 --> 36:30.800
Help me!

37:55.110 --> 37:56.320
Zhuge Yue...

38:00.670 --> 38:01.710
You are Chu Qiao,

38:01.730 --> 38:03.850
not Princess Fu, right?

38:03.920 --> 38:05.250
What are you doing here?

38:06.070 --> 38:08.470
What are you and the Crown Prince
planning?

38:16.190 --> 38:17.030
Li Ce...

38:18.550 --> 38:20.320
Li Ce said I am Princess Fu.

38:22.760 --> 38:23.480
I...

38:24.760 --> 38:25.550
I...

38:35.840 --> 38:36.590
Where is she?

38:57.480 --> 38:59.080
Since you like making deals,

38:59.230 --> 39:00.560
let's make another one.

39:00.630 --> 39:01.320
Mother

39:01.800 --> 39:03.280
seems very certain

39:03.360 --> 39:04.400
that you are Chu Qiao.

39:04.400 --> 39:05.260
Your Highness!

39:05.390 --> 39:07.070
Your Highness, you can't go in!

39:07.070 --> 39:09.110
Everyone knows
the Crown Prince is useless.

39:09.110 --> 39:11.230
So I took the liberty to see you.

39:11.790 --> 39:12.790
Chu Qiao?

39:13.030 --> 39:13.840
Zhao Kuo!

39:14.890 --> 39:15.520
Kill her!

39:15.550 --> 39:16.480
Then let's see

39:17.230 --> 39:18.100
who is faster.
